      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. those are the core pillars, but my students need more depth for a high-level round. can you expand on the 'rule of law' and 'national sovereignty' points? specifically, how do proponents argue that uncontrolled migration isn't just a logistical issue, but a fundamental threat to the social contract and the integrity of the nation-state itself? i want them to have the strongest philosophical ground possible.",
